            "answer_text": "The easiest way to solve such equation is to assign some value to each e.g. a-b = x b-c = y c-a = z In such case x + y + z = 0 The equation comes to (-) z {(x^2 + y^2 - x y)} + z^3 (-) z {(x+y)^2 (-) 3 xy)} + z^3 (-) z (-z)^2 + 3 xyz + z^3 (-) z^3 + 3 xyz + z^3 3 xyz or 3 (a-b)(b-c)(c-a) is the answer ",
